默认在函数中定义的参数都是常量参数，这个参数你只可以查询使用，不能改变它的值
func eat(_ food: String) -> Void {
    food = "Banana" // Error: Cannot assign to value: 'food' is a 'let' constant
    print("eat: \(food)")
}

如果想要声明一个变量参数，可以在参数定义前加 inout 关键字:
func eat(_ food: inout String) -> Void {
    food = "Banana"
    print("\(food)")
}

var food = "watermelon"
eat(&food)

